stink from the river,
you look for my son.

21:59.526 --> 22:02.946
-You know where
your son is now, Grace?
-You can call me Mrs. Morgan.

22:04.656 --> 22:08.368
You got nothin' to talk
to Fred about. And don't
pull any of your sick tricks.

22:08.368 --> 22:11.371
I know how ya put
people in a corner.
Last situation,

22:11.371 --> 22:13.915
