in his apartment.

23:18.855 --> 23:20.357
Oh, my God.

23:22.275 --> 23:25.237
Oh, my God.
BOYD:
Fred needs help.

23:25.779 --> 23:28.698
I would've given him
any money he wanted.

23:33.120 --> 23:35.080
You're messin'
with people's minds.

23:35.080 --> 23:37.624
Artie lived in my home,
and now you're...

23:37.624 --> 23:40.419
makin' him lie like
