23:42.045 --> 23:44.840
-You lived in our home.
-I know. I know.

23:44.840 --> 23:48.468
Oh, God. Oh, God,
how could this happen?

23:48.468 --> 23:51.304
Better calm down, Mrs. Morgan.

23:52.681 --> 23:55.225
Are you gonna hurt him?
Please don't hurt him.

23:55.225 --> 23:58.478
If we have to hunt
your son down, yes,
he might get hurt.

23:58.478 --> 24:01.481
If I say where he is,
w-will ya treat him right?

24:01.481 --> 24:04.151
We don't wanna have to use force
any more than you want us to.

24:04.151 --> 24:08.321
Please,
because it's my fault.

24:08.321 --> 24:10.157
No, Grace.

24:17.664 --> 24:23.086
He's at a condominium
at Breezy Point,
my sister's.

24:23.086 --> 24:25.505
You write down
the address here.

24:25.505 --> 24:29.384
