was his responsibility?

24:31.219 --> 24:32.596
Yeah.

24:35.265 --> 24:36.933
Poor thing.

24:47.527 --> 24:50.655
So who--who turned me in--
that old fart with the rat?

24:50.655 --> 24:51.948
Nah.

24:51.948 --> 24:54.826
I-I'll stay outta
that building, okay?

24:54.826 --> 24:57.621
God, it's, like, such
a big deal. Two of youse--
two detectives.

24:57.621 --> 25:00.040
Been drinkin', Harvey?

25:00.040 --> 25:02.959
Yeah. So?
That's still legal,
isn't it?

25:02.959 --> 25:04.836
-What else do you do
with your time?
