25:04.836 --> 25:07.172
What kind of work?

25:08.548 --> 25:12.511
-Advertising.
-You're an ad man?

25:12.511 --> 25:16.181
-I distribute advertising.
-You mean you
hand out circulars.

25:16.181 --> 25:19.643
-Yeah. That's what I said.
-Who do you work for?

25:19.643 --> 25:23.104
-Place on Broadway.
-"Place."
