25:37.369 --> 25:39.079
I fell behind
on the rent, you know?

25:39.079 --> 25:41.498
And blowin' your
money on crack.

25:41.498 --> 25:44.000
I don't smoke crack. What
do I want with crack?

25:44.000 --> 25:48.838
-How is it workin' around
those nude dancers?
-They're inside. I'm outside.

25:48.838 --> 25:51.550
-You don't mix?
-Money-grubbers, they are.

25:51.550 --> 25:55.804
-Where were you this morning
around 9:30, 10:00?
-Asleep.

25:55.804 --> 25:59.516
-Anybody vouch for that?
-No. I was alone.

25:59.516 --> 26:01.476
Who--Who you gonna show
that picture to?

26:01.476 --> 26:06.731
-Girl in a hospital.
Somebody cut her face up.
-Whoa. Wait a minute.

26:06.731 --> 26:08.817
You didn't--
You never said
nothin' about that.

26:08.817 --> 26:12.237
-I thought this was trespassin'.
-You were hoping
it was trespassin'.

26:12.237 --> 26:14.823
If you're the one
who cut that girl, you can
do yourself some good...

26:14.823 --> 26:16.616
by getting your story out.

26:18.034 --> 26:21.288
Because maybe--
maybe there were circumstances
that caused it to happen...

26:21.288 --> 26:23.790
without you...
intending it to.

26:23.790 --> 26:26.167
Did she lead you on?

26:30.088 --> 26:32.841
-Whoa. I want a lawyer.
-You're requesting a lawyer?

26:32.841 --> 26:35.927
Yeah. Yeah.
You're tryin' to frame me.
