26:35.927 --> 26:39.764
Yeah? He must've
gotten you a walk on one
of those other collars, huh?

26:39.764 --> 26:41.516
I'm not talkin' no more.

27:05.665 --> 27:07.000
(sighs)

27:07.000 --> 27:10.629
