that doesn't affect...

28:53.606 --> 28:55.608
the situation we have here.

28:59.904 --> 29:02.157
Look.
I'll call you back.

29:02.157 --> 29:04.409
Hung himself,
this diamond crook.

29:04.409 --> 29:08.580
-And made a lousy job of it.
-Yeah. Took an eight-foot drop,
tore his head off.

29:08.580 --> 29:10.498
You found the stones?

29:10.498 --> 29:13.710
(snaps fingers)
This close.
Headin' for South America.

29:13.710 --> 29:16.004
All right. Voucher 'em.
Call the owner.

29:16.004 --> 29:20.550
-I'll contact
the mother for the I.D.
