29:58.588 --> 30:01.382
-Nah. I'm okay.
-I'm Detective Sipowicz.
Have a seat.

30:06.513 --> 30:07.889
Smoke?

30:17.357 --> 30:18.983
So, uh--
(clears throat)

30:18.983 --> 30:23.613
this girl that
got her face cut--
know anything about it?

30:23.613 --> 30:27.867
Nothin'. She picked
my picture, she's wrong.
That's all I can say.

30:27.867 --> 30:31.079
-Waitin' for
a lawyer, huh?
-Right.

30:31.079 --> 30:35.500
This waives your right
to an attorney.
