I didn't do it.

30:42.382 --> 30:46.761
-So the girl was mistaken
about you?
-Yeah.

30:46.761 --> 30:50.056
Ow! Ooh!
Leave me alone.

30:50.056 --> 30:53.142
I'm sorry. I, uh--
(chuckles)
