31:40.023 --> 31:41.149
Yeah.

31:42.859 --> 31:44.193
(sighs)

31:44.193 --> 31:46.279
Hey!

31:46.279 --> 31:48.156
-(grunts)
-You cut this girl
just for fun,

31:48.156 --> 31:49.866
didn't you, huh--
you sick son of a bitch?

31:49.866 --> 31:52.744
-Get off of me!
