then she started
fightin' and screamin'.

32:00.793 --> 32:03.046
No!
You lyin' bastard!

32:03.046 --> 32:05.548
-Ah!
-You cut her 'cause she
wouldn't have nothin' to do...

32:05.548 --> 32:08.593
-with a stinkin' turd like you
in a million years.
-(moans)

32:08.593 --> 32:10.970
-Now are you gonna give it up
to me, huh? Are you?
-(moans)

32:10.970 --> 32:13.681
I'm gonna give it up.
I'm gonna give it up.

32:13.681 --> 32:15.892
All right.

32:18.311 --> 32:19.896
All right.

32:24.943 --> 32:29.781
(panting, whimpers)

32:30.156 --> 32:32.659
