32:40.667 --> 32:42.627
(door closes)

32:42.627 --> 32:47.006
So, uh, am I in the wrong
line of work, Andy?

32:47.006 --> 32:49.425
You know, I should've
been a store clerk
or somethin'.

32:49.425 --> 32:52.136
-Cut it out, Medavoy.
-Boss takes me off
of that guy.

32:52.136 --> 32:55.390
Maybe he's right. I-I--
I don't intimidate a skell.

32:55.390 --> 32:58.226
You think we're supposed
to be all one thing, huh?

32:58.226 --> 33:01.562
You got a way
that works for you.
Some skells they, uh--

33:01.562 --> 33:04.691
they need somebody
to listen to 'em, or
they're lookin' for help.

33:04.691 --> 33:07.652
That works for you. Me--

33:07.652 --> 33:10.697
I look like the kinda guy
who's gonna go nuts and jump
all over 'em, so I use that.

33:10.697 --> 33:14.200
Our boss's job--
put the right one of us
on the thing that needs doin'.

33:14.200 --> 33:17.412
Yeah. Well, I-I-I--I feel
I would have gotten there.

33:17.412 --> 33:20.873
It just happens I-I--
I got objections
to tunin' a guy up.

33:20.873 --> 33:25.211
-Everyone's got his methods.
-God--God forbid, somethin'--
somethin' happens in custody.

33:25.211 --> 33:27.797
Don't think
I don't live with that
in the back of my mind.

33:27.797 --> 33:32.427
God forbid, you ask yourself,
"Did--Did he only go 'cause--
'cause he was gettin' hit?"

33:32.427 --> 33:37.473
-That's an absolute,
accurate concern.
-So how do you deal with that?

33:37.473 --> 33:41.310
Kelly had rules:
"Beat no one on spec."

33:41.310 --> 33:45.106
"Know the guy's right
off witness statements
and physical evidence," plus...

33:45.106 --> 33:49.527
"He don't confess,
your witnesses get beat
or killed for testifying."

33:49.527 --> 33:52.989
Me, if I feel I gotta do it,
