34:02.206 --> 34:06.502
that boss that sent me in--
his bottom line's gonna be,
"All I said was a reinterview."

34:06.502 --> 34:09.255
And the people that want me
tunin' this guy up--
if Gina was their family...

34:09.255 --> 34:11.507
so she wouldn't
have to testify--

34:11.507 --> 34:15.178
they'll sit on my jury
at trial and they'll
vote to lock me up.

34:15.178 --> 34:18.347
I better know all that
before I raise a hand.

34:21.309 --> 34:24.645
-Who's this guy writin' for?
-Me.

34:24.645 --> 34:26.272
Yeah.

34:43.164 --> 34:44.415
(door closes)

34:48.086 --> 34:51.589
No. That's, uh, okay,
if you prefer to make
the I.D. tomorrow.

34:53.049 --> 34:58.471
I'll pick you up
at 9:00 tomorrow.
All right, ma'am.

34:58.471 --> 34:59.305
Hi.

35:00.139 --> 35:01.766
-Worked out with your guy?
